### ======================================================================
### AUTHENTICATIE
### ======================================================================

### Registreer een nieuwe gebruiker (voer eenmalig uit per gebruiker)
POST {{apiBase}}/users/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Login om een JWT token te krijgen
# @name loginRequest
POST {{apiBase}}/users/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}


### ======================================================================
### WORKOUT PLANNEN (CRUD)
### ======================================================================

### Maak een nieuw workoutplan aan
POST {{apiBase}}/plans
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Mijn Kracht & Hypertrofie Plan",
  "description": "Een 4-daags Upper/Lower split schema.",
  "isActive": true,
  "workoutTemplates": [
    {
      "name": "Upper Body A",
      "exercises": [
        { "exerciseName": "Bench Press", "order": 1, "targetSets": 3, "targetRepsMin": 5, "targetRepsMax": 8 },
        { "exerciseName": "Pull-up", "order": 2, "targetSets": 3, "targetRepsMin": 6, "targetRepsMax": 10 }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Lower Body A",
      "exercises": [
        { "exerciseName": "Squat", "order": 1, "targetSets": 3, "targetRpsMin": 5, "targetRepsMax": 8 },
        { "exerciseName": "Leg Press", "order": 2, "targetSets": 3, "targetRepsMin": 10, "targetRepsMax": 15 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### Haal alle workoutplannen op voor de ingelogde gebruiker
GET {{apiBase}}/plans
Authorization: {{authToken}}


